songs.title: Nowhere To Go
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Lil Skies]
Ayy
I don't see nobody in this shit, that's all I know
Remember we was broke and we ain't had no where to go
And we ain't had no where to go
(And we ain't had no where to go)
Ayy

[Chorus: Lil Skies]
I don't see nobody in this shit, that's all I know
Remember we was broke and we ain't had no where to go
Said she love me now because I'm stunting at my shows
Money on my mind, I stack it up, can't let it fold
That's my little shorty, think I like her on the low
She bug me all the time, think I be worried 'bout these hoes
I just wrote a gas up to the face then I smoke
Hit it one time and you probably gonna choke

[Verse 1: Lil Skies]
Flexing on these niggas, I don't even mean to brag
Shitting on my enemies, I step out with a bag
You showing your true colors, why you out here lookin' sad?
Broski want a Rari, I'ma cop it, fuck the tag
Out in Cali with a shorty that's from overseas
She said she really love me but she not the one for me
I treat her like a queen, let her live in royalty
Niggas love to hate, but they don't show no loyalty
It's alright, are you the savage type?
I like to catch a vibe, Uber and catch a ride
No, I'ma put it down
King me, give me the crown
No, I'ma fuck it up
So just don't make a sound

[Bridge: Lil Skies]
(So just don't make a sound
So just don't make sound
So just don't make a sound
So just don't make a sound
So just don't make a sound)

[Chorus: Lil Skies]
I don't see nobody in this shit, that's all I know
Remember we was broke and we ain't had no where to go
Said she love me now because I'm stunting at my shows
Money on my mind, I stack it up, can't let it fold
That's my little shorty, think I like her on the low
She bug me all the time, think I be worried 'bout these hoes
I just wrote a gas up to the face then I smoke
Hit it one time and you probably gonna choke

[Verse 2: Landon Cube]
No one, no one
Ever come between me and my play
No one, no one
So it's a family, only family I trust
Roll one, roll one
Smoking fast, getting gassed, 'bouta pass out
All homies all up on me but they backed out
Living fast now, pedal on the gas now
And they don't know how to act now
I just laugh, watching everybody crash down
Living fast now, pedal on the gas down

[Outro: Landon Cube]
Woah, woah
Woah, woah woah
